'''NGC 1398'''是[[天炉座|天炉座]]的一個[[棒旋星系|棒旋星系]]。該星系擁有雙環狀結構，距離地球約6500萬光年<ref name=noao>{{cite web|title=NGC 1398|url=http://www.noao.edu/outreach/aop/observers/n1398.html|website=noao.edu|accessdate=17 February 2015|archive-date=2014-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809003100/http://www.noao.edu/outreach/aop/observers/n1398.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Moore|first1=E. M.|last2=Gottesman|first2=S. T.|title=THE BARRED SPIRAL GALAXY NGC 1398 AND ITS PATTERN SPEED|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|date=1 July 1995|page=159|url=http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?bibcode=1995ApJ...447..159M&db_key=AST&page_ind=0&data_type=GIF&type=SCREEN_VIEW&classic=YES|accessdate=17 February 2015|bibcode=1995ApJ...447..159M|doi=10.1086/175862|volume=447}}</ref>。

== 概要 ==
NGC 1398的直徑為稍大於銀河系的13.5萬光年，內部恆星數量估計超過1千億<ref name=fnal>{{cite web|title=Dark Energy Survey kicks off second season cataloging the wonders of deep space|url=http://www.fnal.gov/pub/presspass/press_releases/2014/Dark-Energy-Survey-20140818.html|website=fnal.gov|accessdate=17 February 2015|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924014144/http://www.fnal.gov/pub/presspass/press_releases/2014/Dark-Energy-Survey-20140818.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該星系於1868年12月17日由德國天文學家{{link-en|弗里德里希·奧古斯特·特奧多爾·溫尼克|Friedrich August Theodor Winnecke}}在[[卡尔斯鲁厄|卡尔斯鲁厄]]發現，當時他正在尋找彗星<ref name="meara">{{cite book|author=Stephen James O'Meara|title=Deep-Sky Companions: Hidden Treasures|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=a6VY0Q1zsJoC&pg=PA110|date=12 April 2007|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-139-46373-7|pages=110}}</ref>。

